===Etymology===
By analogy with the way a snowball collects the more snow in one turn the larger it is, as it rolls down a hillside.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[snowball]] [[effect]]}}

# An [[accelerating]] [[growth]] of magnitude, including [[fame]], [[fortune]], [[importance]], or [[danger]].
